title: Kennedy.2015.05.19.WS.SDTV.x264-XAiO
description:
Kennedy does yet another monologue on Hillary and the email scandal.

Tonight's panel is KATHERINE MANGU-WARD, SHERROD SMALL, and DAGEN McDOWLELL discuss the Clinton email scandal. Chris Christie comes out of the pro-NSA closet to say that Snowden sucks and mass surveillance is great! 

BRYAN SUITS comes by to talk about if the Iraq invasion was a mistake and the 2016 presidential candidates responses to this question. (Spoiler: Rand is the only one that thinks it was a mistake.)

The panel comes back to talk about Pixar's dedication to more diversity. Simon Pegg talks about how Hollywood is dumbing down.

Topical Storm:
Dog plays pingpong.
Real life little Mario.
Idiot robs the wrong bank, gets beat down and duct taped by MMA dude.
Miley Cyrus sings about her dead blowfish.
Harry Styles mini-me.

KATHERINE MANGU-WARD, SHERROD SMALL, and DAGEN McDOWLELL are back to talk about the boy scouts banning water guns over "safety concerns". Taylor Swift is hot, magazine agrees, panel doesn't. Congressman thinks he deserves a raise.

A recent special shows cheating on exams for FAA air traffic control employees. ADAM SHAPIRO is here to discuss said special, "TROUBLE IN THE SKIES".

In tonight's Nightcap Kennedy talks about America's fattest city.
